data.description: This is your chance to live in the desirable Studio Estates gated community! This beautiful custom home sits on over half an acre. Great location. Underground Utilities. Country feel yet minutes from highways, toll roads, shopping centers, restaurants and hospitals. Fast and easy access to Austin/I-35/Airport/Tesla Gigafactory/San Marcos. Quiet and safe community with beautiful hill country views. Community fishing pond and trail.
